{"tid":1295471,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中共的對手, 只有美國","createTime":"2019-07-08T04:39:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T04:42:56.000Z","uid":222140,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7783ed3f5be4d792d93eefd71147f456ddf96e13","tid":1295471,"uid":222140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:39:20.000Z","msg":"陳雲：高舉美國旗請願，寫明歡迎美國國會通過《香港人權及民主法案》，解放香港，要令美國知道香港人民急切期待美國國會的立法，這樣美國才可以出師有名，大力為香港也為美國在香港的利益做事。<br />\n假如遊行之中，美國國旗遭受不禮貌的對待甚至驅趕，會成為國際事件，中共也不會好受。<br />\n由於美國是友邦，高舉美國旗的時候要令美國國旗享有尊嚴。"},{"pid":"6c197ccb2be6d24d4f156ab1d912ffe6dd36fe75","tid":1295471,"uid":268327,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:40:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EgD17zw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEgD17zw.png&h=0d0fa98c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1295142\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1295142</a><br />\n<br />\n集氣推推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f949e42385fcc3969eb94c0d1928707d02b0440d","tid":1295471,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:42:56.000Z","msg":"Ok"}]}